<section id="about">
  <h2>About Us</h2>
  <p>
    <strong>Heretic Hunters</strong> is a nonprofit organization committed to
    defending the truth of the Gospel and helping believers recognize teachings
    that distort or misrepresent God’s Word.
  </p>
  <blockquote>
    “But examine everything carefully; hold fast to that which is good.”
    — 1 Thessalonians 5:21
  </blockquote>
  <p>
    We seek to promote biblical accuracy, spiritual discernment, and steadfast
    faith in a world filled with confusion.
  </p>
</section>

<section id="mission">
  <h2>Our Mission</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Educate:</strong> Teach sound doctrine rooted in Scripture</li>
    <li><strong>Expose:</strong> Examine false teachings with truth and love</li>
    <li><strong>Equip:</strong> Strengthen believers to stand firm in faith</li>
  </ul>
  <blockquote>
    “Watch yourselves, so that you may not lose what we have worked for.”
    — 2 John 1:8
  </blockquote>
</section>

<section id="approach">
  <h2>Our Approach</h2>
  <p>
    We operate with humility and integrity, seeking restoration rather than
    condemnation.
  </p>
  <blockquote>
    “Speaking the truth in love.” — Ephesians 4:15
  </blockquote>
</section>

<section id="join">
